lead_paragraph: Dominique Dillingham scored 12 points, Teaira McCowan added 11 and No. 16 Mississippi State beat Vanderbilt 63-46 in the Southeastern Conference women's tournament Friday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 16 Mississippi State Women Beat Vanderbilt 63-46
